            "speak;Simone;What's the point.{w}{clear}Bring you in the same things happen.{w}{clear}I am always so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so, so stupid.{w}{clear}What I thought -{w}{clear}I'd capture you,{w} present you,{w} get paid from you,{w} get a job,{w}{clear}From the governor,{w} work right,{w} up the ranks,{w} to be governor,{w} so -{w}{clear}Why, do I -{w}{clear}Why am I -{w}{clear}Why do I try?{w}{clear}Like waking up outside a dream I never can remember.{w}{clear}Why am I so far removed from where I want to be?{w}{clear}Why was I when I first started -{w}{clear}Is it even what I thought when -",
