            "mirror_portrait;Simone",
            "speak;Marcel;To the very bitter end you have to see things through.{w}{clear}Even if you don't succeed,{w} you are left with what you lived through.{w}{clear}Something you can hold to use to better what you did.{w}{clear}As long as you keep trying,{w} it won't matter what goes against you.{w}{clear}Even if things don't look good now.{w}{clear}Even if they don't work out at first.",
